    <h1>Seshy Pricing</h1>

    <p>Seshy is a tool for both collaboration and storage.</p>
    <p>It's always free to collaborate on projects.</p>
    <p>You only pay for storage of projects that you own.</p>
    <p>You can collaborate with others by creating teams and sharing projects with them.</p>
    <p>Teams are free, and you can have as many as you need.</p>
    <p>It doesn't cost you anything to contribute to projects that are owned by others.</p>
